## Check packages installed 
### py -m pip list

## Install a specific version of the package called requests
### py -m pip install requests==2.30.0

## Update a package called requests
### py -m pip install -U requests

## Uninstall a pacgage called requests 
### py -m pip uninstall requests 


# Virtual Environment = venv
## to create a virtual enviro
### py -m venv .venv

## activate venv
### source .venv/Scripts/activate

## deactivate env
### deactivate



## to check dependencies a package named requests
### py -m pip show requests

# to find useful python packages
## pypi.org

## create a file with a list of the requirements of this project
### py -m pip freeze > filename.txt